MBOMBELA &#8211; Vantage Goldfields CEO, Mr Mike McChesney, testified during the public inquiry into the disaster, that their investigation revealed illegal mining took place before the mine collapsed.Also read: Is human error behind the collapse at Lily mine? The inquiry started on Monday and is tasked with investigating the underlying causes of the accident.McChesney said Vantage Goldfields did its own investigation before the collapse and found there were a great deal of Zama-Zamas (illegal miners) operating in the area.Also read: Lily Miners recount collapse The inquiry will continue on Wednesday.